Unique X and AUWE Sign Agreement for Movie Transit Deployment in Brazil

=E2=80=8A

Dublin, Ireland =E2=80=93 06th May 2026 =E2=80=93 Unique X, the world-leadi=
ng cinema software and content delivery company, and AUWE, a premier e-deli=
very operator in Brazil, are proud to announce a 5-year strategic agreement=
 for the deployment of the Movie Transit network across the country.

This landmark partnership marks a significant milestone in Unique X's Latin=
 American strategy. By combining AUWE's established local leadership with t=
he Movie Transit network, the collaboration will provide near-complete cove=
rage of the Brazilian market, reducing logistical complexities for both dis=
tributors and exhibitors.

AUWE, which currently connects 423 cinemas and 1,193 screens, projects to d=
ouble its reach within this year. This growth will be powered by the integr=
ation of the Movie Transit infrastructure into=C2=A0AUWE's state-of-the-art=
 operations, ensuring that the highest standards of content delivery are ma=
intained nationwide.

Jos=C3=A9 Eduardo Ferr=C3=A3o, CEO of AUWE, commented: "Excellence in techn=
ology and service defines the essence of AUWE; these are the bricks with wh=
ich we build long-term relationships of trust. Our partnership with Unique =
X is born from a shared dedication to the state-of-the-art. Together, we wi=
ll achieve 100% market coverage, broadening our horizons and deepening the =
confidence our partners have placed in us since 2010 as we move to double t=
he number of screens we serve this year."

Roger Harris, CEO of Unique X, added: "Brazil is=C2=A0a=C2=A0strategic mark=
et for Unique X, and partnering with=C2=A0AUWE=C2=A0was=C2=A0a=C2=A0natural=
 choice given their impeccable track record and technological leadership. T=
his agreement is=C2=A0a=C2=A0testament to our commitment to the Latin Ameri=
can market and our belief in the power of technology to transform cinema op=
erations. We are thrilled to support=C2=A0AUWE=C2=A0in their mission to ach=
ieve total coverage, fully integrating Brazil into the global Movie Transit=
 network, and we are excited to bring the benefits of Movie Transit to Braz=
il's largest cinema operators as we continue our expansion across the regio=
n."

=E2=80=8A

About UniqueX
Unique X is the market-leading brand and product portfolio for the future s=
trategy and innovation of digital cinema, providing intelligent autonomous =
cost-saving solutions and revenue-generating fully managed content services=
. Unique X operates in 100 countries across the globe and excels in deliver=
ing mission-critical cinema software. Advertising Accord currently powers 1=
.1 billion advertising spots annually across 31 territories and 45,000 scre=
ens worldwide. With its fully automated and scalable capabilities, it is tr=
ansforming cinema advertising by providing exhibitors with=C2=A0a=C2=A0comp=
lete end-to-end solution that integrates both traditional and programmatic =
sales. Market-leading cinema solutions include RosettaBridge Eco TMS (Theat=
er Management System), RosettaNet (Circuit Management System), Movie Transi=
t (Digital Cinema Package Content Delivery Network), Basekey (KDM managemen=
t), RosettaLive (Event Streaming), Advertising Accord (Complete Advertising=
 Sales Management and Programmatic Advertising), KDMX (next generation glob=
al KDM services) SmartTrailering (Intelligent Trailer Scheduling) and Uniqu=
e=E2=80=99s unrivalled consumer product, the movie and gaming content priva=
te cinema hire event platform =E2=80=9CBook The Cinema=E2=80=9D.

About=C2=A0AUWE
Founded in 2010,=C2=A0AUWE=C2=A0is=C2=A0a=C2=A0leading S=C3=A3o Paulo-based=
 cinema delivery and post-production company. It operates one of Brazil's l=
argest electronic networks, connecting 420+ cinemas and 46 distributors nat=
ionwide. Specializing in DCP, KDM, and mastering,=C2=A0AUWE=C2=A0provides s=
ecure, state-of-the-art delivery for feature films and trailers.=C2=A0[www.=
auwe.com](http://www.auwe.com/)

